{
  "texts": [
    "ResultsIn our study, we assessed various classification models' effectiveness in predicting crystal system classes for lithium-ion batteries.",
    "The models scrutinized encompassed Support Vector Machine (SVM) [45], Logistic Regression (LR) [46], Naive Bayes (NB) [47], and a Voting Model, amalgamating SVM, LR, and NB.",
    "Additionally, we proposed a novel Deep Neural Network (DNN) approach for comparison.",
    "From the results presented in Table 1, it is evident that the DNN model outperforms the other models across all evaluation metrics.",
    "The DNN achieved a Macro F1-Score of 0.81."
  ]
}